{"tid":1752312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"南昌中發生咩事？","createTime":"2019-11-24T19:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T12:08:40.000Z","uid":302041,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf91e3411a0772b01a4414163b71e84cbfeba3b","tid":1752312,"uid":302041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:45:04.000Z","msg":"【即時】(03:31) 在深水埗「南昌中」選區，經歷過第一輪點票結果後，爭取連任的民建聯劉佩玉取得1,500票，而人稱「深水埗二妹」的民主派林倩同則取得1,501票，二妹以一票之差擊敗劉佩玉。其後劉佩玉要求重新點票，覆核問題選票後，最終的投票結果為劉佩玉以1,640票，擊敗獲1,538票的林倩同。"},{"pid":"0b91994c9e00e4b3c220a0a8444c367b3d2d54dc","tid":1752312,"uid":75105,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:47:32.000Z","msg":"多成百幾票？明眼人都知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c55fe9355558e53b89d648a5d9dffa4432d215d","tid":1752312,"uid":17284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:52:06.000Z","msg":"做假啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3373f29abab243641bd3d354fe52b5c3af69dcc","tid":1752312,"uid":313027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:53:42.000Z","msg":"做假啦，cls"},{"pid":"ae98f74eab2297bffa7433d9d8597dee79bafbb8","tid":1752312,"uid":302041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:54:29.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />突然多成百票"},{"pid":"c7a007bd10aca2a46fb58bd80f91cee1fd0626af","tid":1752312,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:54:55.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"8ad21eb8d3390bc9d0a59e10c757260690d57acd","tid":1752312,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:55:15.000Z","msg